{"tid":2224104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★全球 iCloud、App Store、Apple Music 故障　大量蘋果服務暫停","createTime":"2020-09-30T09:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T10:12:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ebfbe9d8ee16e4028a147a880e6191bdc3493c2","tid":2224104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"今天，如果你發現 App Store、Apple Music 以至 iCloud 服務出現故障，不是你的個别問題，而是 Apple 的問題。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Apple 的系統狀態監察頁面的資料顯示，目前 Apple Store（Mac）、Apple Music、Apple TV+、iCloud 多項服務也曾出現故障，部份至今仍未能使用。遇到這些問題時，相信除了耐心等待外，也沒有方法可解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/09/30/apple-serivce-down/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2Fapple-serivce-down%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=1f597ebe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/09/30/apple-serivce-down/</a>"},{"pid":"60054db496872d3b010fbd40ed3d93262ae1659f","tid":2224104,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAieEyd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAieEyd.gif&h=ac6fd3dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa1c6f017a3a62f692dcf1d1b2b497036253c734","tid":2224104,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e8430c95062cbe56abf647a940b39035393be3","tid":2224104,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"